Package gradescope

Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • gradescope.Order
  • public class Order
extends Object
    Represents an order to buy/sell a product on the market. Each order is for a positive amount of a single product, is either a buy order or a sell order, has a limiting price (maximum for buy, minimum for sell), an invoking trader, and a unique 4 digit hexadecimal id String. Orders remain open until they are finalised or cancelled.
